OL,3,CWoman arrested after Rihanna's LA home
OL,4,Chit by gunshots
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after gunshots
OL,8,Fwere fired at Rihanna's Los Angeles
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,FPolice said no one was hurt in the
OL,12,FSunday afternoon incident. It was not
OL,13,Fclear if the singer was at her home
OL,14,Fwhen the shooting happened.
OL,16,FPolice received a call about shots
OL,17,Fbeing fired around 1.15pm in the
OL,18,FBeverly Hills area, Officer Charles
OL,19,FMiller said on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
