OL,3,CWoman arrested after Rihanna's LA home
OL,4,Chit by gunshots
OL,6,FIvanna Lisette Ortiz, 35, was later
OL,7,Ftaken into custody, and investigators
OL,8,Frecovered a weapon from the scene.
OL,10,FLocal television reports showed video
OL,11,Fof what appeared to be five bullet
OL,12,Fholes in the front gate of the home.
OL,14,F"Shooting just occurred. Ten gunshots
OL,15,Ffired from the vehicle," a police
OL,16,Fdispatcher told responding officers on
OL,17,Faudio obtained by KABC-TV. The gunfire
OL,18,Fcame from across the street, police
OL,19,Fsaid.
