OL,3,CWoman arrested after Rihanna's LA home
OL,4,Chit by gunshots
OL,6,FIt was not known if the woman under
OL,7,Farrest had any connection to Rihanna.
OL,9,FIn 2018, a man was accused of breaking
OL,10,Finto a different home of Rihanna's in
OL,11,Fthe Hollywood Hills and spending 12
OL,12,Fhours there.
OL,14,FThe man pleaded no contest to felony
OL,15,Fcounts of stalking and vandalism and a
OL,16,Fmisdemeanour count of resisting arrest
OL,17,Fin 2019. He was sentenced to probation.
