OL,3,CWoman arrested after Rihanna's LA home
OL,4,Chit by gunshots
OL,6,FA nine-time Grammy Award winner,
OL,7,FRihanna has 14 Number one hits on the
OL,8,FBillboard Hot 100, including "We Found
OL,9,FLove," "Work," "Umbrella" and
OL,10,F"Disturbia." She founded the makeup
OL,11,Fbrand Fenty Beauty in 2017.
OL,13,FShe and A$AP Rocky announced the birth
OL,14,Fof their third child, a girl named
OL,15,FRocki Irish Mayers, in September.
